{"tid":998479,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[完成曹星如宏願] 中國再誕拳王！徐燦12回合挫對手贏世界拳王羽量級金腰帶","createTime":"2019-01-28T04:14:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-28T10:23:33.000Z","uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f8e5b241ddffdabc9492d5452865f2cc7140d131","tid":998479,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T04:14:46.000Z","msg":"中國拳手徐燦周日（27日）在美國休斯敦舉行的WBA世界拳王金腰帶爭霸賽中，成功擊敗現任羽量級世界拳王羅哈斯（Jesus Rojas），贏得羽量級金腰帶，成為繼熊朝忠、鄒市明之後，中國第3位世界拳王。 <br />\n<br />\n徐燦在比賽經驗上不及波多黎各人羅哈斯，今次只是第2次在美國比賽，但他賽前已提早到美國集訓。羅哈斯之前曾豪言，要在6個回合內KO徐燦，但徐燦的防守做得非常好，不給對方機會。但羅哈斯的腳步和出拳速度很快，從第6、7回合開始羅哈斯開始發起攻擊。 <br />\n<br />\n雙方打足12個回合，點數更一度逼近，最終裁判一致判定徐燦獲勝。年僅24歲的他現時是中國最年輕的世界職業拳王。 <br />\n<br />\n徐燦與羅哈斯一戰，被世界權威數據網站Boxrec（世界拳擊檔案網）評為4星級比賽。徐燦目前在WBA羽量級官方世界排名中位列第2，此前已取得12連勝，近3場比賽2次擊敗對手。羅哈斯則有26勝2負2平、19次擊敗對手的彪炳戰績。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190127/mobile/bkn-20190127140935741-0127_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190127%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190127140935741-0127_00952_001.html&d=WJDHSNsNXgcyXkOr%2BhNZvB4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=08d60709\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190127/mobile/bkn-20190127140935741-0127_00952_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RuxrAet.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRuxrAet.png&h=82035746&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MVSGo7P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMVSGo7P.png&h=fc035670&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b6c338ef5286c9cef798a9544022acee57eecc40","tid":998479,"uid":220431,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T04:35:14.000Z","msg":"食左咩新藥"},{"pid":"476615cc4d3472f71ee98102fad0da5b76a39118","tid":998479,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T10:23:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C6qHU36.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC6qHU36.png&h=6a2082ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YVwHaCs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYVwHaCs.png&h=cfad3699&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}